This paper deals with the development of a neural network model that can perform complex relational reasoning, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model is based on deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing (NLP) techniques, which is a subfield of computer science that deals with the interaction between computers and human language (cs.CL). Additionally, the model is applied to image recognition tasks, which is a common application of computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper mentions the use of recurrent neural networks, which are a type of neural network commonly used in the field of neural engineering (cs.NE).
